---
description: 'SaaS client application requirements'
---

***definitions***

- :API: is the API of the 3rd party SaaS service.

- :ListOfUsers: is the list of users of the 3rd party SaaS service.

- :APIDocs: are the docs of :API:.

***test reqs***

- :ConformanceTests: should use real :API: server - do not use mock server.